<sec id="id-6615ee61-a373-483a-9615-fdf827282320"><title><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="7b63f686-64aa-45c3-b124-c298e5eb6cff" timestamp="1656532517655"?>Identifying stakeholders<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="7b63f686-64aa-45c3-b124-c298e5eb6cff"?></title><p><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="53a001a3-f0f0-4516-94b3-df33b75dd85f" text=" " timestamp="1670337094060"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="0956d2a4-c688-4f4c-e4d7-97d4e58543c5" timestamp="1656532510287"?>Stakeholders are <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="0956d2a4-c688-4f4c-e4d7-97d4e58543c5"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="3c4bc6df-f55a-43d1-acc9-8a8dbd2cfe8a" text="organizations or individuals that have one or more interests in any decision or activity of an organization. " timestamp="1670256189606"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="0c6012e7-8415-4bde-fc7a-364f2df8ca67" timestamp="1670337118307"?>individuals or groups that has an interest in any decision or activity of an organization.<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="0c6012e7-8415-4bde-fc7a-364f2df8ca67"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="1e013431-0aa1-46a4-b84d-1e51d3079209" text="Because these interests can be" timestamp="1670337118305"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="5191008" change-id="09c8eb23-4dba-4be8-d254-b7535bd0693a" text=" affected" timestamp="1665949652766"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="2b3b4580-b6e0-4b93-8c24-2fc2af4791c1" text=" influenced by an organization, a relationship with the organization is created. This relationship " timestamp="1670337118306"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="5191008" change-id="5175039d-0ba0-4727-e7f9-9b56f396e450" text="n" timestamp="1665949866218"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="f1c1a81f-0745-417c-87cb-c283cd93a593" text="can " timestamp="1670337118306"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="5191008" change-id="5b2250ec-5d37-4d21-f02a-f8ed8558d1ab" text="eed not " timestamp="1665949871247"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="133883e2-1f2e-4524-ff55-9939849e7baf" text="be formal or unformal." timestamp="1670337118307"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="b38b23af-3c8a-4f67-eb67-41957224f8c5" timestamp="1670337119089"?> <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="b38b23af-3c8a-4f67-eb67-41957224f8c5"?>Understanding how individuals or groups are or can be affected by an organization's decisions and activities will make it possible to identify the interests that establish a formal or unformal relationship with the organization. Therefore, the organization's determination of the impacts of its decisions and activities will facilitate identification of its most important stakeholders.</p><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="88c552c6-9267-454c-ed98-c493a2608117" timestamp="1656532510287"?>Organizations may have many stakeholders. Some stakeholders are internal to the organization. They <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="88c552c6-9267-454c-ed98-c493a2608117"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="ffb796ce-3b5e-4fb9-fab7-851391d68e29" timestamp="1670337186362"?>should <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="ffb796ce-3b5e-4fb9-fab7-851391d68e29"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="267dba97-37e8-4cee-f394-2e0d5e93c565" timestamp="1656532510287"?>include,<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="267dba97-37e8-4cee-f394-2e0d5e93c565"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="744657f2-27c8-4e71-8a18-2c33da12230e" text=" for example" timestamp="1670337188715"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="be03994e-2d04-4ace-9fea-b17f48ff24b2" timestamp="1670337192337"?> but are not limited to<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="be03994e-2d04-4ace-9fea-b17f48ff24b2"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="5c8b47b1-30d3-4006-c8a3-64796b648233" timestamp="1656532510287"?>, the organization’s members, workforce, contractors or <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="5c8b47b1-30d3-4006-c8a3-64796b648233"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="a34fa7ba-5200-4bc5-8c5a-766700b9ef05" timestamp="1670333504469"?>governing <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="a34fa7ba-5200-4bc5-8c5a-766700b9ef05"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="833d4404-40ed-475b-db3f-2df16deb0b93" text="executive " timestamp="1670333505270"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="81b8e881-2a8c-4fd9-cd46-7c084c38fd1f" timestamp="1656532510287"?>bodies. They may also include workers' committees, internal to the organization, and trade unions, external to the organization. Other stakeholders are external to the organization. They <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="81b8e881-2a8c-4fd9-cd46-7c084c38fd1f"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="51793f56-a61a-4150-881c-939584dcd0a9" timestamp="1670337214244"?>could <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="51793f56-a61a-4150-881c-939584dcd0a9"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="319a4bd8-6aa2-473d-f1b5-e036ea7f3c94" timestamp="1656532510287"?>include, <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="319a4bd8-6aa2-473d-f1b5-e036ea7f3c94"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="f2ffc071-2300-4805-ea2c-8f07b80e1337" text="for example" timestamp="1670337211689"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="6317dd2e-3a87-49cf-8391-a0acf05c4575" timestamp="1670337211690"?>but are not limited to, <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="6317dd2e-3a87-49cf-8391-a0acf05c4575"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="c60b0c90-5544-433a-be37-1c423b08ad81" text=", " timestamp="1670337218173"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="28ea51f7-f912-413e-f88f-d0527007ba9d" timestamp="1656532510287"?>customers, suppliers, the public or local authorities and the associations with which the organization interacts.<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="28ea51f7-f912-413e-f88f-d0527007ba9d"?></p><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="22178560-b6b8-4ddc-d485-3818e248dffe" timestamp="1656532510287"?>To identify stakeholders and better understand their ecosystem, the organization should <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="22178560-b6b8-4ddc-d485-3818e248dffe"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="a4f0e898-a6f7-482a-b717-18f05b93c9f6" text="ask itself " timestamp="1666188935864"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="bf238cfb-642c-4b1e-acf1-4b7b10e0cf25" timestamp="1666188945281"?>consider <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="bf238cfb-642c-4b1e-acf1-4b7b10e0cf25"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="74424eae-b9bf-4ce6-d590-8ccbcd21d518" timestamp="1656532510287"?>the following questions:<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="74424eae-b9bf-4ce6-d590-8ccbcd21d518"?></p><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="baf64209-d6e1-4226-e840-1e0b1bfc67e7" timestamp="1656532510286"?>—    To whom does the organization have legal obligations?<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="baf64209-d6e1-4226-e840-1e0b1bfc67e7"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="03a883e4-b7d1-4666-93a3-202a7ad57ace" timestamp="1667481361912"?> To whom are there no legal obligations?<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="03a883e4-b7d1-4666-93a3-202a7ad57ace"?></p><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="0864d6dc-a755-4805-e579-db97ccb42a82" timestamp="1656532510286"?>—    Who might be positively or negatively affected by the organization's decisions or activities?<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="0864d6dc-a755-4805-e579-db97ccb42a82"?></p><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="7a4d399f-adf3-407c-a613-10bef4364bdd" timestamp="1656532510286"?>—    Who is likely to express concern<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="7a4d399f-adf3-407c-a613-10bef4364bdd"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="07f55d19-9cad-48a5-f1ac-b16719b161cb" text="s" timestamp="1666189055953"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="0b217a68-3764-4bcc-bce8-c97bb6e56f0d" timestamp="1656532510286"?> about the decisions and activities of the organization?<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="0b217a68-3764-4bcc-bce8-c97bb6e56f0d"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="89d6b4be-ec0c-41d4-c455-c82ed17655e7" timestamp="1667481384975"?> Who are likely to be impacted, but does not raise concern?<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="89d6b4be-ec0c-41d4-c455-c82ed17655e7"?></p><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="7bdae8c5-c7ec-446b-ca2d-c88301c44e16" timestamp="1656532510286"?>—    Who has been involved in the past when similar concern<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="7bdae8c5-c7ec-446b-ca2d-c88301c44e16"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="6116ff5d-0bd3-4c23-fa46-454d7e011895" text="s" timestamp="1666189071312"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="5c387b07-39a4-4973-bd1f-20ce43832a10" timestamp="1656532510286"?> needed to be addressed?<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="5c387b07-39a4-4973-bd1f-20ce43832a10"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="cede983d-243e-4cba-f73c-26d9824355c1" timestamp="1667481431370"?> Who were not involved who likely have these concerns?</p><p>—    Who can help the organization address specific impacts?</p><p>—    Who can affect the organization's ability to meet its responsibilities?</p><p>—    Who would be disadvantaged if excluded from the engagement?</p><p>—    Who in the value chain of the service and/or product is affected? Are they affected differently?<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="cede983d-243e-4cba-f73c-26d9824355c1"?></p><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="0a02b8ed-9d8a-4d1f-d125-b31748d8619c" timestamp="1656532510286"?>—    Who can help the organization address specific impacts?<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="0a02b8ed-9d8a-4d1f-d125-b31748d8619c"?></p><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="9ac75648-c906-4914-bfd8-80ca09f6da77" timestamp="1656532510286"?>—    Who can affect the organization's ability to meet its responsibilities?<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="9ac75648-c906-4914-bfd8-80ca09f6da77"?></p><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="5896e2ad-8c76-4e67-e41c-8c12f61729dc" timestamp="1656532510286"?>—    Who would be disadvantaged if excluded from the engagement?<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="5896e2ad-8c76-4e67-e41c-8c12f61729dc"?></p><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="ccc0bfe4-0db3-49cc-fe6a-0e9fbaaf79fb" timestamp="1656532510286"?>—    Who in the value chain of the service and/or product is affected<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="ccc0bfe4-0db3-49cc-fe6a-0e9fbaaf79fb"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8848353" change-id="a147ade6-c213-422e-d877-aedcfaf53fa9" timestamp="1670337351503"?> positively or negatively?</p><p>The organisation should consider the gender parity within the group of identified stakeholders.</p><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="a147ade6-c213-422e-d877-aedcfaf53fa9"?><p/></sec>